snippet.title: Super Vadimka VI A Terrible Threat there is No Vadimka Announcement Trailer 2023
snippet.description: Super Vadimka VI A Terrible Threat there is No Vadimka - a computer game in the genre of action and platformer developed by VadimBallzGame is the last part of the games in the series announced on January 1, 2023 for the New Year. Super Vadimka is the only sixth part that should be released on PlayStation in the sixth part we see the 16-bit hero Vadimka quite cool as well as the mechanics of the ability of bosses and enemies. Dr. Kulechek escaped from a mental hospital he was released 1 year ago, well, he still returned to start the last battle with the main character.
